            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "These are of the same form as the ones for Camassa-Holm equation [2], and indeed every equation in the so-called \u2018b-family\u2019 of equations that the Degasperis-Procesi and Camassa-Holm equations belong to has such solutions [4].",
